the bank:

Try reinstalling.

This isn’t windows It’s been updated a few times since strange stuff started to happen, so it has been re-installed.

[quote=“Mopman, post:13, topic:360579”]nginx time?

But uh, I don’t see how the latest thing could be lightys fault :S[/quote]

I don’t either, but it definitely was, since a restart on just the webserver fixed it. It’s got to be some type of caching error that is occurring, and stuff like that that isn’t reproducible is damn near impossible to track down.
